Description: The Human Development Report Office (HDRO) of the United Nations Development Programme (UNDP), produces the global Human Development Report, which features the Human Development Index (HDI). Also available is the Human Development Research Paper (HDRP) Series, which is a medium for sharing recent research commissioned to inform the global Human Development Report, which is published annually, and further research in the field of human development. The authors include leading academics and practitioners from around the world, as well as UNDP researchers.
